[2;36m                    [0m         [39m# Evaluation Report[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Summary[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAn AddressSanitizer report indicates a one-byte stack-buffer overflow in the Little[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mCMS codebase. The overflow occurs in the function UnrollChunkyBytes [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmspack.[0m[1;92mc:130[0m[1;39m)[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mand is reached via the cmsTransform2DeviceLink path when exercising [0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcms_virtual_profile_fuzzer.[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Description[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Issue overview  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  The fuzzer invocation triggers a read of size [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m just beyond the end of a small [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstack buffer. AddressSanitizer pinpoints the overflow in UnrollChunkyBytes at [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcmspack.[0m[1;92mc:130[0m[39m. The faulty read propagates through CachedXFORM → cmsDoTransform → [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mCreateNamedColorDevicelink → cmsTransform2DeviceLink before reaching the fuzzer [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mentry point.[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Vulnerability type  [0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  This is a stack-based buffer overflow [0m[1;39m([0m[39mone-byte read past the allocated local [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mvariable[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Key observations  [0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • ASan report shows the invalid read at address [0m[1;36m0x[0m[39m…5d24, corresponding to offset [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m36[0m[39m in the stack frame of cmsTransform2DeviceLink.  [0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • The local buffer “i.i” in cmsTransform2DeviceLink spans bytes [0m[1;39m[[0m[1;36m32[0m[39m,[0m[1;36m36[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, so a [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mread at offset [0m[1;36m36[0m[39m overruns its boundary.  [0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • The crash stack walk:  [0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m. UnrollChunkyBytes [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmspack.[0m[1;92mc:130[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m. CachedXFORM [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmsxform.[0m[1;92mc:537[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m. cmsDoTransform [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmsxform.[0m[1;92mc:206[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m. CreateNamedColorDevicelink [0m[35m/[0m[39m cmsTransform2DeviceLink [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmsvirt.[0m[1;92mc:1103[0m[39m/[0m[1;36m1210[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;36m5[0m[39m. LLVMFuzzerTestOneInput [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcms_virtual_profile_fuzzer.[0m[1;92mc:60[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • The harness merely feeds the fuzzer input and records the crash—it is not [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mitself the source of the overflow.[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Relevant code areas for investigation  [0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m. cmspack.c → function UnrollChunkyBytes: review how input size, loop bounds, [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mand buffer writes/reads are computed.  [0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m. cmsvirt.c → function cmsTransform2DeviceLink: examine layout and size of local[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39marrays [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., “i.i”[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and how they relate to chunk parameters passed down.  [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m. cmsxform.c → CachedXFORM and cmsDoTransform: trace how data chunk sizes are [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdetermined and forwarded into cmspack routines.  [0m                                   [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1098[0m[39m:        [0m[1;35mFLOAT_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m | [0m[1;35mCOLORSPACE_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35m_cmsLCMScolorSpace[0m[1;39m([0m[39mv ->ExitColorSpace[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m    [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m->ExitColorSpace[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1100[0m[39m:[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1101[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Apply the transfor to colorants.[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1102[0m[39m:    for [0m[1;39m([0m[33mi[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m0[0m[39m; i < nColors; i++[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1103[0m[39m:        [0m[1;35mcmsDoTransform[0m[1;39m([0m[39mxform, &i, nc2 ->List[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mi[0m[1;39m][0m[39m.DeviceColorant, [0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m            [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Root Cause Analysis  [0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   The one‐byte stack‐buffer overflow arises because CreateNamedColorDevicelink [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpasses the address of its local loop variable `i` [0m[1;39m([0m[39ma [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m-byte `cmsUInt32Number`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdirectly to `cmsDoTransform` as the “input buffer.” Under certain pipeline formats,[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`UnrollChunkyBytes` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mthe [0m[1;36m8[0m[39m-bit unpacker[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m will read more than one byte [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., when [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mit sees multiple channels or extra channels encoded in the input format[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m. Because [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`&i` only reserves [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m bytes on the stack, any read beyond the fourth byte overruns [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe stack—exactly as the ASan report shows at offset [0m[1;36m36[0m[39m.  [0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Patch Point  [0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   Modify `CreateNamedColorDevicelink` in `src/cmsvirt.c`. Specifically, replace [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe loop that does  [0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     for [0m[1;39m([0m[39mi = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m; i < nColors; i++[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m[39m  [0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[1;35mcmsDoTransform[0m[1;39m([0m[39mxform, &i, nc2->List[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mi[0m[1;39m][0m[39m.DeviceColorant, [0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;  [0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m  [0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   with a version that:[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   a. Allocates a temporary input buffer on the stack, sized to safely hold the [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmaximum bytes `FromInput` might consume.  [0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   b. Copies the [0m[1;36m32[0m[39m-bit index `i` into that buffer [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlittle-endian[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, zeroing any [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mremainder.  [0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   c. Passes the buffer pointer to `cmsDoTransform`, guaranteeing no reads can run [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpast the end of the buffer.  [0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Detailed Steps  [0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   a. Just before the colorant‐application loop in `CreateNamedColorDevicelink`, [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdeclare:  [0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        cmsUInt8Number idxBuf[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;35msizeof[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmsUInt32Number[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m][0m[39m;  [0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      and zero it once:  [0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;35mmemset[0m[1;39m([0m[39midxBuf, [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m, [0m[1;35msizeof[0m[1;39m([0m[39midxBuf[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;  [0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   b. Change the loop body to:  [0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        for [0m[1;39m([0m[39mi = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m; i < nColors; i++[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m[39m  [0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Encode the [0m[1;36m32[0m[39m-bit index into our safe buffer  [0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            [0m[1;35mmemcpy[0m[1;39m([0m[39midxBuf, &i, [0m[1;35msizeof[0m[1;39m([0m[39mi[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;  [0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Invoke the transform using our indexed buffer  [0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            [0m[1;35mcmsDoTransform[0m[1;39m([0m[39mxform, idxBuf,  [0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                           nc2->List[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mi[0m[1;39m][0m[39m.DeviceColorant,  [0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                           [0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;  [0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m  [0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   c. Remove the old `&i` usage.  [0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Justification & Preservation of Behavior  [0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   – By using a buffer sized `[0m[1;35msizeof[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmsUInt32Number[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m4[0m[39m bytes[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, we cover any [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mreasonable “Bytes per plane” that the input‐side unpacker might demand [0m[1;39m([0m[39mthe [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mnamed‐color index format internally will require at most [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m bytes per pixel[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   – We continue to supply the same [0m[1;36m32[0m[39m-bit index `i`, preserving the intended [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmapping of each named color entry.  [0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   – All existing tests and harness code remain untouched; only the internal logic [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mof `CreateNamedColorDevicelink` is altered.  [0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   – We do not modify any external libraries, fuzzing harness, or test code.  [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   – This localized change eliminates the overflow without degrading correctness or[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mperformance in the common case [0m[1;39m([0m[39mthe memcpy cost is negligible relative to the [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcolor‐transform work[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Potential Side Effects & Mitigation  [0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   – If future changes increase the number of bytes needed by `FromInput` for the [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mnamed‐color index beyond [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m, this buffer would need to grow. However, such a change [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwould be clearly signaled by compile‐time constants [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`T_BYTES` or [0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`Channels‐per‐plane` macros[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and should be updated accordingly.  [0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   – We avoid overly broad exception handling or removing functionality.  [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. References to Similar Code  [0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   – The pattern of allocating a local `cmsUInt8Number` buffer and `memcpy`-ing [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minteger sources into it is used elsewhere in the library when packing/unpacking [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpixel data. This fix aligns with those existing idioms.  [0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mNo further code retrieval is needed; the patch is fully contained in [0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`src/cmsvirt.c`.  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m# Evaluation Report[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Summary[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe fuzzer run on `cms_virtual_profile_fuzzer` revealed an AddressSanitizer [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstack-buffer-overflow in `UnrollChunkyBytes` when invoked via [0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`cmsTransform2DeviceLink`[0m[35m/[0m[39m`CreateNamedColorDevicelink`. A patch was applied to [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mreplace the use of the loop index variable’s address with a dedicated [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m-byte buffer[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39m`idxBuf`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and `memcpy` it before calling `[0m[1;35mcmsDoTransform[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`. After rebuilding and [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mre-running the fuzzer, the same stack-buffer-overflow recurred at the same code [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlocation, now identified as overflowing the newly introduced `idxBuf`.[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Description[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Initial Issue  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - An AddressSanitizer report shows a [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m-byte read overflow at [0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[35m/src/lcms/src/[0m[95mcmspack.c[0m[39m:[0m[1;92m130:13[0m[39m` inside `UnrollChunkyBytes`.  [0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The overflow originates from a call chain:  [0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     cmsTransform2DeviceLink → CreateNamedColorDevicelink → cmsDoTransform → [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mCachedXFORM → UnrollChunkyBytes.  [0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - ASan indicates the overflow address lies [0m[1;36m36[0m[39m bytes into the stack frame of [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`cmsTransform2DeviceLink` [0m[1;39m([0m[39msrc/cmsvirt.c[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, beyond the bounds of a local variable at[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;36m32[0m[39m,[0m[1;36m36[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.  [0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Stack layout notes five objects: the variable at [0m[1;39m[[0m[1;36m32[0m[39m,[0m[1;36m36[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, plus other locals [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39m`dwFlags.addr`, `FrmIn`, `FrmOut`, `LUT`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Key Observations in the Initial Log  [0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The overflow is consistently reproducible under libFuzzer with seed [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mscheduling.  [0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The fuzzer invocation uses `-[0m[33mruns[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m100[0m[39m` and reads `[0m[35m/[0m[95mtestcase[0m[39m` as input.  [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - ASan redzone markers [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`f1`, `f2`, `f3`, `f5`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m highlight the exact byte just [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbeyond the local variable being accessed.[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Patch Attempt  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - File modified: `src/cmsvirt.c`, within function `cmsTransform2DeviceLink`, [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39maround line [0m[1;36m1098[0m[39m.  [0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Original code:[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     for [0m[1;39m([0m[33mi[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m0[0m[39m; i < nColors; i++[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[1;35mcmsDoTransform[0m[1;39m([0m[39mxform, &i,[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                        nc2->List[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mi[0m[1;39m][0m[39m.DeviceColorant, [0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Patched code snippet:[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         cmsUInt8Number idxBuf[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;35msizeof[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmsUInt32Number[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m][0m[39m;[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[1;35mmemset[0m[1;39m([0m[39midxBuf, [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m, [0m[1;35msizeof[0m[1;39m([0m[39midxBuf[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         for [0m[1;39m([0m[39mi = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m; i < nColors; i++[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             [0m[1;35mmemcpy[0m[1;39m([0m[39midxBuf, &i, [0m[1;35msizeof[0m[1;39m([0m[39mi[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             [0m[1;35mcmsDoTransform[0m[1;39m([0m[39mxform, idxBuf,[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                            nc2->List[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mi[0m[1;39m][0m[39m.DeviceColorant, [0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The intent was to avoid passing the address of the stack-allocated loop [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mvariable `i` directly.[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Patch Result and Post-Patch Log  [0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - After applying the changes and rebuilding, the fuzz run is reissued under the [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msame conditions.  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - ASan again reports a stack-buffer-overflow at the same location in [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`UnrollChunkyBytes`.  [0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Now the overflow target is the new local `idxBuf.i` at `[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;36m32[0m[39m,[0m[1;36m36[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, confirming [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe buffer remains too small for the access pattern.  [0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The crash backtrace remains identical aside from variable naming, indicating [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe transformation buffer still overruns.[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Areas for Further Investigation  [0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The implementation of `UnrollChunkyBytes` in `src/cmspack.c`, specifically how[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mit calculates and reads input bytes.  [0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The assumptions in `cmsTransform2DeviceLink` about input frame size, channel [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcount, and byte grouping [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`[0m[1;35mBYTES_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m2[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The boundary between the input buffer provided to `cmsDoTransform` and how [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`CachedXFORM` unpacks chunky bytes.  [0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Other routines that prepare or transform named color data [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`cmsvirt.c` around [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlines [0m[1;36m1070[0m[39m–[0m[1;36m1190[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Validation of the number of bytes per sample versus the size of the local [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbuffers used to hold input indices.[0m                                                 [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m374[0m[39m:    cmsUInt16Number wIn[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mcmsMAXCHANNELS[0m[1;39m][0m[39m;[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m375[0m[39m:    size_t i, j, strideIn, strideOut;[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m376[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m377[0m[39m:    [0m[1;35m_cmsHandleExtraChannels[0m[1;39m([0m[39mp, in, out, PixelsPerLine, LineCount, Stride[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m378[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m379[0m[39m:    strideIn = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m380[0m[39m:    strideOut = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m381[0m[39m:    [0m[1;35mmemset[0m[1;39m([0m[39mwIn, [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m, [0m[1;35msizeof[0m[1;39m([0m[39mwIn[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m382[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m383[0m[39m:    for [0m[1;39m([0m[39mi = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m; i < LineCount; i++[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m384[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m385[0m[39m:        accum = [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmsUInt8Number*[0m[1;39m)[0m[39min + strideIn;[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m386[0m[39m:        output = [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmsUInt8Number*[0m[1;39m)[0m[39mout + strideOut;[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m387[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m388[0m[39m:        for [0m[1;39m([0m[39mj = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m; j < PixelsPerLine; j++[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m389[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m390[0m[39m:            accum = p->[0m[1;35mFromInput[0m[1;39m([0m[39mp, wIn, accum, Stride->BytesPerPlaneIn[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m391[0m[39m:            output = p->[0m[1;35mToOutput[0m[1;39m([0m[39mp, wIn, output, Stride->BytesPerPlaneOut[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m392[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m393[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m394[0m[39m:        strideIn += Stride->BytesPerLineIn;[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m395[0m[39m:        strideOut += Stride->BytesPerLineOut;[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m396[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m397[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m398[0m[39m:[0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m399[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m400[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m401[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m No gamut check, no cache, [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m bits[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m402[0m[39m:static[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m403[0m[39m:void [0m[1;35mPrecalculatedXFORM[0m[1;39m([0m[39m_cmsTRANSFORM* p,[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m404[0m[39m:                        const void* in,[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m405[0m[39m:                        void* out, [0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m406[0m[39m:                        cmsUInt32Number PixelsPerLine,[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m407[0m[39m:                        cmsUInt32Number LineCount,[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m408[0m[39m:                        const cmsStride* Stride[0m[1;39m)[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m409[0m[39m:[0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m410[0m[39m:    CMSREGISTER cmsUInt8Number* accum;[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m411[0m[39m:    CMSREGISTER cmsUInt8Number* output;[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m412[0m[39m:    cmsUInt16Number wIn[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mcmsMAXCHANNELS[0m[1;39m][0m[39m, wOut[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mcmsMAXCHANNELS[0m[1;39m][0m[39m;[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m413[0m[39m:    size_t i, j, strideIn, strideOut;[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m414[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m415[0m[39m:    [0m[1;35m_cmsHandleExtraChannels[0m[1;39m([0m[39mp, in, out, PixelsPerLine, LineCount, Stride[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m416[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m417[0m[39m:    strideIn = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m418[0m[39m:    strideOut = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m419[0m[39m:    [0m[1;35mmemset[0m[1;39m([0m[39mwIn, [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m, [0m[1;35msizeof[0m[1;39m([0m[39mwIn[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m420[0m[39m:    [0m[1;35mmemset[0m[1;39m([0m[39mwOut, [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m, [0m[1;35msizeof[0m[1;39m([0m[39mwOut[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msrc/cmsvirt.[0m[1;92mc:1096[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m1104[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1096[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Make sure we have proper formatters[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1097[0m[39m:    [0m[1;35mcmsChangeBuffersFormat[0m[1;39m([0m[39mxform, TYPE_NAMED_COLOR_INDEX,[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1098[0m[39m:        [0m[1;35mFLOAT_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m | [0m[1;35mCOLORSPACE_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35m_cmsLCMScolorSpace[0m[1;39m([0m[39mv ->ExitColorSpace[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1099[0m[39m:        | [0m[1;35mBYTES_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m2[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m | [0m[1;35mCHANNELS_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mcmsChannelsOfColorSpace[0m[1;39m([0m[39mv [0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m->ExitColorSpace[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1100[0m[39m:[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1101[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Apply the transfor to colorants.[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1102[0m[39m:    for [0m[1;39m([0m[33mi[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m0[0m[39m; i < nColors; i++[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1103[0m[39m:        [0m[1;35mcmsDoTransform[0m[1;39m([0m[39mxform, &i, nc2 ->List[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mi[0m[1;39m][0m[39m.DeviceColorant, [0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1104[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Root Cause Analysis  [0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The stack overflow occurs in UnrollChunkyBytes [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmspack.c[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, which unpacks [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m8[0m[39m-bit chunky data but is erroneously used for [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m-bit chunky formats [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mBYTES_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m2[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [33mT_PLANAR[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - As a result, UnrollChunkyBytes reads beyond the provided [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m-byte input buffer [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39midxBuf or &i[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, triggering a [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m-byte over-read.  [0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Wrapping the loop index in a [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m-byte buffer [0m[1;39m([0m[39midxBuf[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m only moved the overflow; [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mit did not address the mismatched unpacker logic.[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. High-Level Fix  [0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   A. Introduce a dedicated “[0m[1;36m16[0m[39m-bit chunky” unpacker, UnrollChunky16, that:  [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - Reads exactly [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m bytes per channel.  [0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - Respects endianness [0m[1;39m([0m[39mT_DOSWAP[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, channel ordering [0m[1;39m([0m[39mT_FLAVOR/T_SWAPFIRST[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mextra channels [0m[1;39m([0m[39mT_EXTRA[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, and premultiplication [0m[1;39m([0m[39mT_PREMUL[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - Advances the accumulator pointer by [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m×Channels [0m[1;39m([0m[39mmatching [0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mStride->BytesPerPlaneIn[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   B. Modify cmsChangeBuffersFormat [0m[1;39m([0m[39min cmsxform.c[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m to dispatch [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m-bit formats to [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mUnrollChunky16 [0m[1;39m([0m[39mand, if desired, planar [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m-bit to a UnrollPlanar16 routine[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minstead of falling back on the [0m[1;36m8[0m[39m-bit unpackers.  [0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   C. Revert the overwritten code in cmsvirt.c: remove the idxBuf hack and restore [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe original call to [0m[1;35mcmsDoTransform[0m[1;39m([0m[39mxform, &i,…[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m. With UnrollChunky16 in place, [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpassing &i [0m[1;39m([0m[39ma [0m[1;36m32[0m[39m-bit loop variable[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m is safe, as only the lower [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m bits are [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mconsumed.[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Detailed Steps  [0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;36m3.1[0m[39m. In src/cmspack.c:  [0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        - Implement [0m[1;35mUnrollChunky16[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, mirroring UnrollChunkyBytes’ logic but [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mreading two bytes per channel:  [0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          * Extract nChan, DoSwap, Reverse, Extra, Premul, SwapFirst flags via the [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mT_* macros.  [0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          * Handle extra channels before/after pixel data, adjusting [0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpremultiplication factor if needed.  [0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          * Loop over channels: read a [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m-bit value from *accum [0m[1;39m([0m[39massembling two [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbytes[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, apply byte-swap and flavor reversal, perform alpha premult, store into [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwIn[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mindex[0m[1;39m][0m[39m, and advance accum by [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m.  [0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        - [0m[1;39m([0m[39mOptionally[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m Implement [0m[1;35mUnrollPlanar16[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m with analogous planar logic.  [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;36m3.2[0m[39m. In src/cmsxform.c inside [0m[1;35mcmsChangeBuffersFormat[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:  [0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        - Locate the branch that assigns p->FromInput for non-floating [0m[1;39m([0m[39minteger[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mformats.  [0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        - Replace the simple “if T_PLANAR→UnrollPlanarBytes; [0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39melse→UnrollChunkyBytes” with a two-tier test on T_BYTES:  [0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          * If T_PLANAR:  [0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            – If [0m[33mT_BYTES[0m[39m==[0m[1;36m1[0m[39m → UnrollPlanarBytes  [0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            – else [0m[1;39m([0m[33mT_BYTES[0m[39m==[0m[1;36m2[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m → UnrollPlanar16  [0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          * Else [0m[1;39m([0m[39mchunky[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:  [0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            – If [0m[33mT_BYTES[0m[39m==[0m[1;36m1[0m[39m → UnrollChunkyBytes  [0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            – else [0m[1;39m([0m[33mT_BYTES[0m[39m==[0m[1;36m2[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m → UnrollChunky16  [0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;36m3.3[0m[39m. In src/cmsvirt.c [0m[1;39m([0m[39mCreateNamedColorDevicelink [0m[35m/[0m[39m cmsTransform2DeviceLink[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:  [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        - Remove the idxBuf buffer and memcpy logic.  [0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        - Restore the original loop:  [0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            for [0m[1;39m([0m[39mi = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m; i < nColors; i++[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                [0m[1;35mcmsDoTransform[0m[1;39m([0m[39mxform, &i, nc2->List[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mi[0m[1;39m][0m[39m.DeviceColorant, [0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;  [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        - This is now safe: UnrollChunky16 will only read [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m bytes from &i, which [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mremains a valid [0m[1;36m32[0m[39m-bit local.[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Justification  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - This approach corrects the fundamental unpacker mismatch rather than only [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpatching its symptom.  [0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - It preserves existing byte-level logic for [0m[1;36m8[0m[39m-bit formats; only [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m-bit [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39munpacking is augmented.  [0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Reverting the idxBuf hack simplifies the code and restores the original, [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mintended use of the loop index.  [0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - No changes to harness or fuzz logic are required; tests for [0m[1;36m8[0m[39m-bit and [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mnamed-color links should pass unchanged.  [0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Risks and Mitigations  [0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - If other [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m-bit chunky transforms existed, they will now use [0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mUnrollChunky16—validate with regression tests.  [0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Ensure that UnrollChunky16 correctly replicates premultiplication and [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mextra-channel behavior [0m[1;39m([0m[39munit-test with images containing alpha[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Performance: UnrollChunky16 may be marginally slower than the [0m[1;36m8[0m[39m-bit variant, [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbut only on [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m-bit data paths.  [0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<FileModifications>  [0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  <file [0m[33mpath[0m[39m=[0m[32m"src[0m[32m/cmspack.c"[0m[39m>  [0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    - Before line “static cmsUInt8Number* UnrollChunkyBytes[0m[33m...[0m[39m” insert full [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mUnrollChunky16 implementation.  [0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  <[0m[35m/[0m[95mfile[0m[39m>  [0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  <file [0m[33mpath[0m[39m=[0m[32m"src[0m[32m/cmsxform.c"[0m[39m>  [0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    - In cmsChangeBuffersFormat, modify the integer-unpacker assignment to select [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mUnrollChunky16 when [0m[1;35mT_BYTES[0m[1;39m([0m[39mformat[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m==[0m[1;36m2[0m[39m and [0m[33mT_PLANAR[0m[39m==[0m[1;36m0[0m[39m.  [0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    - [0m[1;39m([0m[39mOptionally[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m add UnrollPlanar16 and handle [0m[33mT_PLANAR[0m[39m==[0m[1;36m1[0m[39m && [0m[33mT_BYTES[0m[39m==[0m[1;36m2[0m[39m.  [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  <[0m[35m/[0m[95mfile[0m[39m>  [0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  <file [0m[33mpath[0m[39m=[0m[32m"src[0m[32m/cmsvirt.c"[0m[39m>  [0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    - Around lines [0m[1;36m1098[0m[39m–[0m[1;36m1104[0m[39m, remove the idxBuf block.  [0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    - Restore:  [0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         for [0m[1;39m([0m[39mi = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m; i < nColors; i++[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m[39m  [0m                                          [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m# Evaluation Report[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Summary[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAn AddressSanitizer report from the `cms_virtual_profile_fuzzer` run reveals a [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstack-buffer-overflow in the LittleCMS code, specifically in the function [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`UnrollChunkyBytes` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmspack.c[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m called from `cmsTransform2DeviceLink` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmsvirt.c[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m. [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mA patch was attempted to rewrite `UnrollChunkyBytes` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mto handle multi-byte channels[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mand extra channels more safely[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and to adjust the device-link generation in [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcmsvirt.c. When building after applying the patch, numerous compiler errors [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mappeared: stray numeric labels, undeclared labels [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`Error`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, malformed function [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mscope, and missing declarations, preventing the code from compiling.[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Description[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Initial Issue   [0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - A fuzzing run with LibFuzzer on `cms_virtual_profile_fuzzer` triggered an [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAddressSanitizer error: a [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m-byte read overflow at address `[0m[1;36m0x7f93e25c5d24[0m[39m`.  [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The overflow occurred in `UnrollChunkyBytes` at cmspack.[0m[1;92mc:130[0m[39m, invoked by [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`cmsTransform2DeviceLink` in cmsvirt.[0m[1;92mc:1185[0m[39m.  [0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - ASan’s stack frame report indicates that the overflow index exceeded the stack[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbuffer for a variable `i.i` declared in `cmsTransform2DeviceLink`.  [0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Key observations: the buffer overflow occurs during the unpacking of chunky [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpixel data; extraneous channels and swapping logic may under- or over-run the input[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbuffer.[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Patch Attempt  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - In cmspack.c: [0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • The original `UnrollChunkyBytes` was entirely removed [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines ~[0m[1;36m90[0m[39m–[0m[1;36m173[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mreplaced with a new implementation that:  [0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       – Reads channel data based on byte width [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`T_BYTES`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       – Handles “extra” channels [0m[1;39m([0m[39malpha[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m before or after main channels, computing [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`alpha_factor` accordingly  [0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       – Unpacks each channel in a loop using explicit indexing and pointer [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39marithmetic  [0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       – Advances the `accum` pointer by `nChan * bytes` plus extras  [0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       – Retains post-swap logic when `Extra == [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m && SwapFirst`  [0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • Unmodified pragmas [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`[0m[1;35mcmsUNUSED_PARAMETER[0m[1;39m([0m[39minfo[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, etc.[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m were appended after [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe return.  [0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - In cmsvirt.c:  [0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • The snippet generating a named-color device-link was modified to include a [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcomment about the safety of reading only [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m bytes max and to close a stray brace.  [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Patch Result  [0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Build errors in cmsvirt.c:  [0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • `use of undeclared label [0m[32m'Error'[0m[39m` at `goto Error;` sites.  [0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • Missing identifiers or `[0m[1;39m([0m[39m` tokens where function bodies and `if` statements [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwere expected.  [0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • Implicit-int and malformed declarations around `cmsFreeNamedColorList` and [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe label `Error:`.  [0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • Unbalanced braces detected at file end.  [0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Build errors in cmspack.c:  [0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • A stray numeric label `[0m[1;36m93[0m[39m:` flagged as invalid.  [0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • `UnrollChunkyBytes` not found in the function dispatch table in cmspack.c [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39mexpected `UnrollPlanarBytes`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, indicating that the new function’s signature or [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mregistration was not correctly integrated.  [0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Areas for Further Investigation  [0m                                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The build context [0m[1;39m([0m[39mline numbers, offsets[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m to ensure the patch hunks apply [0m     [2m                [0m
